# Smart Retail Analytics System

## Overview

The Smart Retail Analytics System is an end-to-end data analytics project developed using Python and Microsoft Power BI. It analyzes retail sales data to generate meaningful business insights through customer segmentation, market basket analysis, sales forecasting, and interactive dashboards.

## Technologies Used

- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Scikit-learn
- mlxtend
- Microsoft Power BI

## Project Modules

- Data Cleaning & Preprocessing
- Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
- Customer Segmentation (RFM Analysis + K-Means Clustering)
- Market Basket Analysis (Apriori Algorithm)
- Sales Forecasting (Linear Regression)
- Interactive Power BI Dashboards

